  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Perform day-to-day general accounting duties</li></ul><ul><li>Input accounting entries in ABSS</li></ul><ul><li>Assist in preparing & monitoring of Grant applications</li></ul><ul><li>Reconciliation & preparation of balance sheet schedules</li></ul><ul><li>Process payments to both internal & external parties</li></ul><ul><li>Maintain Accounts Payable & Receivable</li></ul><ul><li>Maintain Fixed Assets sub-ledger</li></ul><ul><li>Filing and archiving of documents</li></ul><ul><li>Assist in all HR & Admin related matters</li></ul><ul><li>Assist in ad-hoc assignments when required </li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Certificate in Accounting (CAT) with at least 2 years in handling full sets of accounts</li></ul><ul><li>Proficient in ABSS & Microsoft Office Applications is preferred</li></ul><ul><li>Independent, committed, hardworking and analytical</li></ul><ul><li>Meticulous with attention to details</li></ul><ul><li>Able to multi-task and work under tight deadlines</li></ul><ul><li>Candidate must be a Singaporean or Singapore PR</li></ul>",
